Label: IL2RG
Comment: IL-4 induces the formation of a complex consisting of IL-4 receptor alpha and common gamma chain.

Label: PIK3CD
Comment: IL-4 induces the interaction of PIK3CD,PIK3CA with PIK3R1,PIK3R2 in human neutrophils.

Label: RASA1
Comment: IL-4 stimulation leads to tyrosine phosphorylation of DOK2 and subsequent interaction of DOK2 with N-terminal SH2 domain of RASA1 in 32D cells.
